Trade/Device Name(s): EGENS One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Kit (Strip)
EGENS One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Kit (Cassette)
EGENS One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Kit (Midstream I)
EGENS One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Kit (Midstream II)
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for EGENS One Step HCG Urine Pregnancy Test Kits for qualitative detection of hCG in urine using chromatographic immunoassay formats (strip, cassette, midstream) for early pregnancy detection.
Indications for Use Summary: Qualitative detection of human Chorionic Gonadotropin (hCG) in urine samples to aid in the early detection of pregnancy by professional and home users.
